{
  "stem": "107.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And of course, freezing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was winter by then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had no good clothes, and minimal food, full of fleas.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was a general saying there that you can do it for a maximum-- a maximum of four weeks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Then you are finished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we know this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They said.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then comes the next transport for the next four weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "People [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I mean this we understood from all the little information.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You know there are always some older persons who have some have some position, and know what the newcomers doesn't know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And so-- so we know, if we are lucky, that maybe the war ends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That could have easily happened, but it didn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And really after four weeks, I had the famous kind of infection in my legs, which usually that get [INAUDIBLE] to general infections.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I knew that was it-- much longer I can not do this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I had all kinds of ideas what to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But nothing was practical in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So one morning I didn't go to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I said, we'll see what happens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I can't anymore.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] is extremely strenuous and cold and hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And in comes one of the doctors, Dr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Goldstein, who was in very early personnel of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And he had-- he was from Poland, had started in Paris, and was with these early transports of foreigners transported to Auschwitz from Paris, or wherever he was-- and somehow survived all the critical moments and worked as doctor in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And had met me there in the last station, the central hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, what's the matter with you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said, [INAUDIBLE] pretty much that's the end of my strength.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I give up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, oh come on.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
